| Block      | Type       |
| ---------- | ---------- |
| `[ ]`      | filter     |
| `\d`, `\w` | predefined |
| `.`        | any char   |
| `+ * {}`   | quantity   |

VERY IMPORTANT

[a-z]+ → lowercase (1 or more)
\d{3} → exactly 3 digits

Golden Rules (Mind la fix panniko)
✅ Rule 1:

👉 [ ] → always one block

✅ Rule 2:

👉 + * {} → previous block ku apply aagum

✅ Rule 3:

👉 . ≠ dot
👉 \. = dot

✅ Rule 4:

👉 always final ah:
“full string meaning enna?”
